2025-12-18: Version 2.2-0 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Re-implementing horizontal mode in plot() functions which got lost
  in the changes for versions 2.0-0 and 2.1-0
  In this context: additional optional parameter arrowtail for plot()
* New function kmbasisfringe(), kmbasisinnerfringe(), kmbasisouterfringe(),
  and kmbasisneighbourhood() mimplementing the algorithm by Hockemeyer
  (1997, JMP)

2025-11-21: Version 2.1-0 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* New functions kmlearningpaths() and kmgradations()
* New utiity function kmsetiselement()
* New method plot.kmneighbourhood()
* New method kmbasis.kmsurmisefunction()
* Fixed bug in kmiita2SR for isolated items in surmise relations
* Vignette updates
* Including PHSG data

2025-10-24: Version 2.0-0 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Introducing classes for KST objects
* kmbasis() S3 method
* New functions kmiita2SR()
* Reworking of the graphical functions; plot() S3 method, obsoleting
  the old functions kmbasisdiagram(), kmSRdiagram(), and kmhasse()
* include flag for kmneighbourhood() and kmnneighbourhood()
* Some bug fixes around column naming

2025-09-30: Version 1.3-0 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Added functions for probabilistic knowledge assessment
* New utility function kmdoubleequal()

2025-04-02: Version 1.2-0 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Documentation updates
* Additional functions kmSRdiagram & kmSRvalidate
* Extending the xpl data set by two components sf and sr (surmise
  function and surmise relation)

2025-01-26: Version 1.1-0 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* New function kmgenerate()

2024-10-03: Version 1.0-1 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Re-implmenting kmsurmisefunction() partially re-using the kmbasis() C code.
* Copying colnames in kmunionclosure from orginal to computed structure.

2024-08-26: Version 1.0-0 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Re-implementing the computationally intensive functions
  kmunionclosure(), kmdist(), and kmbasis() in C.

2023-10-12: Version 0.2-0 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Adding kmsurmisefunction() (requiring packages sets and pks)
* Setting horizontal default to FALSE in kmhasse() and kmbasisdiagram()
* Adding kmbasisdiagram()

2023-01-23: Version 0.1-5 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Adding kmeqreduction()

2022-10-24: Version 0.1-4 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Refining kmhasse()
* Adding kmnneighbourhod()

2022-03-24: Version 0.1-3 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Adding kmhasse() based on Wai Wong's waiplot()) function

2019-06-09: Version 0.1-2 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Optimized kmunionclosure() and kmsurmiserelation()
* Deleted kmconstrDowling()
* All data are in integer format now

2019-03-27: Version 0.1-1 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Corrected a bug in kmvalidate()

2018-09-10: Version 0.1-0 (Cord Hockemeyer, cord.hockemeyer@uni-graz.at)
* Creation of the package
